      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, and it drives perfectly. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is the one for you. Can't wait for it to find a great new home!",
